				"§72. §eMechanical Press§7 directly above it, connected to a powered shaft."
				"§73. §eMechanical Arm§7 feeding ingredient items onto the Press input."
				"§7   The Arm pulls from a §eIngredient Chest§7 holding glyph materials."
				"§74. §eBrass Funnel§7 below the Press collects finished glyphs → §eOutput Chest§7."
				""
				"§eIngredient planning:§r"
				"§7• §eGlyph Projectile§7 — 1 Archwood Log + 1 Source Gem."
				"§7• §eGlyph Harm§7 — 2 Archwood + 1 Nether Wart + 1 Source Gem."
				"§7• §eGlyph Amplify§7 — 2 Archwood + 1 Glowstone + 1 Source Gem."
				"§7• §eGlyph Extend Time§7 — 2 Archwood + 1 Chorus Fruit + 1 Source Gem."
				"§7• §eSource Gem§7 supply from your §eSource-from-rotation§7 system (prev quest)."
				""
				"§eSequenced production:§r"
				"§7• §eCreate Sequenced Assembly§7 can produce different glyphs in batches."
				"§7• §eDeploy§7 Archwood → §ePress§7 with Source Gem → §eRepeat§7 N times"
				"§7  using §eSequenced Gearshift§7 for precise batch control."
				""
				"§eSaturation with Source:§r"
				"§7• Source Jar feeding via §eStarbuncle§7 or §eCreate-to-Source§7 covers"
				"§7  the Glyph Press Source consumption automatically."
				"§7• 1 Starbuncle Wheel cycle = ~32 Glyph crafts before Source runs low."
				""
