			description: [
				"§6The Source Dynamo§f is a demonstration of the complete Ars Creo loop:"
				"§7magic powers machines, machines power magic, indefinitely."
				""
				"§eThe full closed loop:§r"
				""
				"§e[Magic → Rotation]§r"
				"§7• §eStarbuncle§7 charges the §eStarbuncle Wheel§7 → outputs §eCreate rotation§7."
				""
				"§e[Rotation → Source]§r"
				"§7• §eCreate shaft§7 → §eArs Creo Source Converter§7 → fills §eSource Jars§7."
				""
				"§e[Source → Magic]§r"
				"§7• §eSource Jars§7 feed §eSpell casting§7, §eFamiliar familiars§7,"
				"§7  and §eRitual automation§7 (Drygmy farms, Whirlisprig tree regeneration)."
				""
				"§e[Magic → Rotation, continued]§r"
				"§7• §eSource Jars§7 also top up §eStarbuncle§7 patrol energy,"
				"§7  keeping the §eWheel spinning§7."
				""
				"§eThe loop is self-sustaining§r §ewhen Source net input ≥ output.§r"
				"§7• §e1 Starbuncle Wheel§7 + §e32 RPM shaft§7 + §e2 Source Jars§7"
				"§7  = roughly break-even Source budget."
				"§7• §e2 Wheels§7 + §e64 RPM§7 = net positive Source — spells and automation"
				"§7  draw from the overflow."
				"§7• Add §eWater Wheels§7 or §eSteam Engine§7 to the same shaft = §elarger"
				"§7  Source overflow§7 for heavier spell loads."
				""
				"§eFull system check:§r"
				"§7• §eJade§7 on Starbuncle Wheel — should show §eRPM: 16+§7."
				"§7• §eJade§7 on Source Converter — should show §econverting: yes§7."
				"§7• §eJade§7 on Source Jar — should show §efilling§7."
				"§7  All three active = loop is closed."
				""
				"§a► Run all three stages simultaneously. Mark done when the loop sustains itself."
			]
